{"tid":1127304,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[電子零件]用90個法拉電容去做大能量的電池,請電容的知識","createTime":"2019-04-27T04:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T11:13:58.000Z","uid":184332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8686845f0c497ec7ed9fc92239623338c7164061","tid":1127304,"uid":184332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:19:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的,因為之前的線圈槍做好了但是火力太少,1M的距離都無(2個2200UF400V電容),所以想用手上90個法拉電容串聯243v來供電.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再看看網上的片見到電容爆炸有問題出現,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請問點計算電容最大的電流和電壓極限?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法拉電容要用什麼方法確保不會過充和接反?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有請大家指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPS:香港人要DIY好困難,找零件因為規格比較特別,所以對方一開始便認定玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7fbe3cbcc2928643d4c200edddde9ae61c06393","tid":1127304,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:32:34.000Z","msg":"黃台仰果枝？"},{"pid":"bae8f6153d51f2bdc0f6758f77cb5c31ba6f08ad","tid":1127304,"uid":92664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:26:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.taobao.com/search?ie=utf8&amp;initiative_id=staobaoz_20190427&amp;stats_click=search_radio_all%3A1&amp;js=1&amp;imgfile=&amp;q=%E4%B8%87%E7%94%A8%E8%A1%A8%E9%92%B3%E5%BD%A2&amp;suggest=0_6&amp;_input_charset=utf-8&amp;wq=%E4%B8%87%E7%94%A8%E8%A1%A8&amp;suggest_query=%E4%B8%87%E7%94%A8%E8%A1%A8&amp;source=suggest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.taobao.com%2Fsearch%3Fie%3Dutf8%26initiative_id%3Dstaobaoz_20190427%26stats_click%3Dsearch_radio_all